						               													<description>Create a new human's history!&amp;#10;You become leaders of human beings, and lead them to the perfect paradise with 52 great men.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each players picks out 1 card from their hands, and the biggest number card wins.&amp;#10;However all cards have different special abilities, and these make complex strategy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Repeat 10 times that putting 1 card from hands.&amp;#10;In the end, a player with the largest sum of paradise points will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are forced to choose which cards to put out in a very limited choice, whether to offer additional as support, or not to take out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is a game that you can play freely many times with 50% luck, 50% strategy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;---STORY---&amp;#10;- The purpose of humankind is to be happy -&amp;#10;- The place where is satisfied all, we will call &amp;quot;Heaven&amp;quot; -&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is the universe of the parallel world.&amp;#10;On the Earth there, a new history of mankind was about to begin.&amp;#10;Great persons who lead people are born in different century, and struggle to make a new history over and over, to bring humankind into the heaven.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The era of the game starts from the 1st century, and it will end in the 10th century.&amp;#10;The players become leaders of humankind, to develop humankind with great persons, and to guide people to the heaven.&amp;#10;Eventually the player who get the highest total of heaven point will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;---Game flow---&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Deal cards&amp;#10;     Place 1 card face down&amp;#10;     Face up card or pass +1&amp;#10;     Influence&amp;quot;Struggle&amp;quot;&amp;#10;     Support (You can add Power. But supporter's Influence does not activate and does not remain in History)&amp;#10;     Winner determined&amp;#10;     Influence &amp;quot;Victory&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;Defeat&amp;quot;&amp;#10;     One winner remains in History&amp;#10;     To the next century&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(At the end of the 10th century, player who have the highest total of Heaven win in this game)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
